==Description==
'''Abomasite''' is a [[Mega Evolution#Mega Pokémon|Mega Stone]] that is used in combination with a Key Stone to [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolve]] Abomasnow into Mega Abomasnow.

==Requirements==
In order to Mega Evolve Abomasnow into Mega Abomasnow, 14,200 attack must first be attained on Abomasnow through breeding.  Once Abomasnow has 14,200 or more attack, using a [[Key Stone]] on it will cause it to Mega Evolve into Mega Abomasnow.  

